    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "people don't get it though. they just say things like \"it gets better\" because they don't want to deal with how dark it actually is. i'm just so tired of the noise and the constant effort to exist in a society that feels like it's rejecting me. it feels like there's no version of the future where i'm not just exhausted and lonely. it almost feels like the only way to actually stop the weight is to just... stop. is it even wrong to want everything to just be quiet?",
